Program communicates with phone via Bluetooth. Running in loop:
	- one of signals switches between modes:
		- 'photo mode'
		- 'video mode'
		- 'motion detector video mode'
	- second after click takes a photo/video

PINS (BCM numbering):
	- [27] (LED) indicates switching between modes
	- [22] (LED) indicates taking a photo/video
	- [18] input from motion detector